author: jleroux
msg: [OFBIZ-4559] Fixed issue: InventoryWorker.getOutstandingProductQuantities returns inaccurate results when there are multiple ItemIssuances for an order, created new view entity called ItemIssuanceQuantitySum. This view entity will have sum of issued item grouped by orderItem of Order. Then this view entity is used in OrderItemQuantityReportGroupByProduct view entity instead of ItemIssuance entity. By doing this, we get accurate results.
